--- !u!114 &6647413043718964586
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 7401447039338378120}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c8acada22c850f94eade910da8c1c087, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  quest2ID: 2
  quest3ID: 3
  stepIndex: 3
  promptPanel: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueCanvas: {fileID: 0}
  dialoguePanel: {fileID: 0}
  npcPortrait: {fileID: 0}
  mariaSprite: {fileID: 0}
  npcNameTMP: {fileID: 0}
  npcNameLegacy: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueBodyTMP: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueBodyLegacy: {fileID: 0}
  nextButton: {fileID: 0}
  nextButtonLabelTMP: {fileID: 0}
  nextButtonLabelLegacy: {fileID: 0}
  openingLines:
  - "You made it! Leona said she'd send someone \u2014 I'm glad it's you."
  - I'm Maria. I've been holding this position for two days now.
  - "That portal \u2014 the one right behind me \u2014 it appeared out of nowhere."
  - At first it was just strange lights. Then the creatures started coming through.
  - My unit has been fighting around the clock. We can stop what comes out, but we
    can't close it.
  - Something on the other side is keeping it open. Someone has to go in and destroy
    it.
  - "My soldiers are exhausted. I can't send them in \u2014 they've given everything
    already."
  - But you... you're fresh, and you're strong. I can feel it.
  - Please. Go through that portal and put an end to this. We'll hold the line as
    long as we can.
  quest3Lines:
  - You made it! I wasn't sure the teleport was still working properly.
  - I'm glad you're here. This situation is... worse than I reported.
  - We pushed forward after the City Gate was secured, but this new gate appeared
    overnight.
  - It's larger. Whatever came through the last one, this one is hiding something
    bigger.
  - I've got soldiers holding the perimeter, but no one willing to go inside. Can't
    blame them.
  - But you and I both know someone has to.
  - Go in. Do what you did at the last gate. End it.
  - I'll be right here when you come back.
  reminderLines:
  - "The dungeon gate is right ahead. Don't hesitate \u2014 we are counting on you!"
  typewriterEffect: 1
  typewriterSpeed: 0.03
  playerTag: Player
